name: Alpine White on a Friday Night
description:
Opening day. Off-field, outside the park, beyond
the gates, something was burning.

The first of this 1/1 collection. 

Utility: 
For those that obtain 3 different 1/1s from this collection, you will be entered into a raffle to win a piece from my main account   "mizz".

For those that hold 5 different mints of this collection, you will receive a digitally created image of their vehicle of choice. Once you have completed obtaining 5 pieces, contact me via Twitter @Mizz_NFT
